matrix.db
Class AccessConstants

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--matrix.db.AccessConstants
Direct Known Subclasses:
Access
public class AccessConstants
extends java.lang.Object

The eMatrix AccessConstants class defines constants used by the Access class. The various static int's, i.e. cRead, cAll, cNone, are well known values that can be passed to the eMatrix Collaboration Kernel when checking access rights.

See Also:
